{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Many applications need to analyze or process the text that they are working with. With so many languages in the world this can be a daunting task. Learn how to process and analyze text in world-ready ways. See how to use the linguistic APIs offered on both iOS and OS X to iterate through text, evaluate regular expressions, and do linguistic analysis of the text you operate on."}],"kind":"article","schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc12-215-text-and-linguistic-analysis"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by reading the transcript and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12-215-Text-and-Linguistic-Analysis","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"roleHeading":"WWDC12","title":"Text and Linguistic Analysis","modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"role":"sampleCode"},"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"overridingTitle":"Read Transcript","type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2012\/215\/"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"sections":[],"references":{"WWDC12-Icon.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"WWDC12-Icon.png","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC12-Icon.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null},"https://nonstrict.eu/wwdcindex/wwdc2012/215/":{"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdci